Class DecoratorLabel

java.lang.Object

      openblocks.renderable.DecoratorLabel
All Implemented Interfaces:
KeyListener, MouseListener, MouseMotionListener, EventListener
public class DecoratorLabel
extends BlockLabel

Provides a label which renders in the top left of a block to inform users what the block type is without using the "label" of the block, which is often user-editable.
